{"tid":722404,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[Princess Principal點算] 聲優今村彩夏宣佈6月末徹底引退停止一切活動","createTime":"2018-06-29T13:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T12:43:05.000Z","uid":6752,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d390ea954f0025c94ccaa4a0bf9edaac69366c","tid":722404,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"動畫《Princess Principal》之前宣佈將推出續作劇場版分成6章上映，大家都期待著安潔和公主的故事繼續下去<br />\n不過今天安潔的聲優今村彩夏宣佈自己將在6月末徹底引退停止一切活動，原因是從去年開始身體健康出現問題無法集中工作<br />\n包括《Princess Principal》續作動畫、手遊在內，很多今村彩夏參與配音的作品之後都要更換聲優了<br />\n這些手遊和《Princess Principal》之後都應該要宣佈聲優更換的消息<br />\n今村彩夏這次的引退非常突然，6月末引退6月29日發佈公告，引退的原因是說今村彩夏從去年開始感覺身體健康出現問題，難以集中精力工作，在各種煩惱後決定選擇引退<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294fdf3223b6fc89f00c4ac9e097a18c07e0c9a4","tid":722404,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"乜水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e7e846daf875ea3aa250262641599c2a7686c3","tid":722404,"uid":125203,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:58:31.000Z","msg":"大肚"},{"pid":"c32ed4e44083fe74f68d3d3e0751df510fc3685d","tid":722404,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcef31697cf07488a7c4075a9c228d4c9e8aeab","tid":722404,"uid":59163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531cdd9c2f97a177bccc513eb0c42419b826d97a","tid":722404,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ohw.ooo/husky/huskyitdog2.gif\" data